The tutorial ends without a practical explanation on how to use the model. How would I take a set of given values (i.e., "age", "workclass", "fnlwgt", "education", "education_num", "marital_status", "occupation", "relationship", "race", "gender", "hours_per_week", "native_country") and predict income_bracket?
